title: Larry Clark- Another Day on Paradise (1998)
description: Another Day In Paradise, the new film from acclaimed director Larry Clark (Kids) is a sexy and thrilling portrayal of a makeshift family of professional thieves on a cross-country crime spree. James Woods (Mel) and Melanie Griffith (Sid) give outstanding performances as the scheming couple who "adopt" two young lovers (Bobby and Rosie), brilliantly played by Vincent Kartheiser and Natasha Gregson Wagner, into their renegade family in order to teach them the ropes of criminal life.
